<title>USA: Amtech Systems hires financial consultant.</title>
<headline>Amtech Systems hires financial consultant.</headline>
<dateline>TEMPE, Ariz. 1997-04-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>Amtech Systems Inc, a maker of equipment used in the production of semiconductors, on Wednesday said it has BC Capital Corp as its merger and acquisition consultant.</p>
<p>&quot;Management is committed to completing one or more acquisitions to further the company's growth strategy,&quot; J.S. Whang, president and chief executive officer, said in a statement.</p>
<p>Miami-based BC Capital Corp will provide advice on acquisitions, mergers and joint ventures.</p>
